{{etymid|ja|くそ}}
{{ja-kanjitab|くそ|y=k|alt=屎,クソ}}
{{IPAfont|⟨kuso<sub>1</sub>⟩}} → {{IPAchar|/kuso/}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|-|sort=くそ}},<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref><ref name=ONCOJKuso>{{R:jpx:ONCOJ|entry=kuswo|number=L051363}}</ref> from {{inh|ja|jpx-pro|*kuso|sort=くそ}}.

Cognate with {{m|ja|臭い|tr=kusai||stinky, smelly}}, {{m|ja|腐る|tr=kusaru||to rot, to become stinky}}.<ref name="KDJ"/>

====Pronunciation====
{{ja-pron|くそ|acc=2|dev=1|acc_ref=DJR,NHK}}

